reviewText: I bought this DVD after watching a few minutes of it from a friend and I loved it. The story was actually interesting, the voice actresses were hot, and so were the girls in the movie. If you're into this kind of stuff (I think you know what I mean) then you'll love this DVD.

reviewText: Animation quality is average. Scenes tend to be on the short side. Story, though cohesive, tends to fill in holes abrubtly and without much thought. Some amusing dialogue. All in all, its okay but nothing to get excited over.

reviewText: This was great. One of the most satisfying titles I own - keep a tissue box close by guys, it will get good use from this one. In total, there were only four sex scenes though, the last two being rather short. That's my only complaint - could have used a few more sex scenes, but it's all good.

reviewText: I read other review that clammed it was like a Slide Show. Well that I could not agree with more. This put a poor quality on the DVD to me but with that said it tries hard NOT to make it a boring slide show and id say they have done well. Story is kinda funny, its more SOFT CORE and personally I liked that. Its not "rapy" like most others iv seen on Amazon. With its price, poor quality, Soft Core'ness I would recommend it but I have a large collection and I would not start your collection with such a low quality hentai.If your a Newbie/ you should keep looking or come back later.If your a Veteran/ Get it just to have it in your collection but dont expect a lot.
